                                    Vision
                                </h2>
                                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                                    The FEU Tech Library aims to be the center of excellence in providing knowledge and quality information, supporting the College's commitment to produce quality individuals in the field of Engineering and Information Technology.
                                </p>
