                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-gold">•</span> Fiction books maybe loaned for a week and subject for renewal for another week if not in demand.Reference and Reserve Books, Periodicals, Vertical Files, Audio-Visual materials, Kindle (E-books), and Undergraduate Research Collection are restricted for library/room use only.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-gold">•</span> Loan period of books end one (1) week before the start of the final examinations.</li>
