                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Materials returned late are subject to overdue fine of Php 8.00/book/day. Overdue Fine Slip is signed by the librarian before payment is made to the Cashier.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Borrowers with overdue books and outstanding obligations will not be allowed to borrow unless all library accounts are settled.</li>
