                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> A lost book while out on loan must be reported immediately to the Librarian.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Lost book must be replaced by the borrower with the same title and edition and pay the accumulated fines.</li>
                                        </ul>
