                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-gold">•</span> Photocopying of undergraduate research/thesis is strictly prohibited.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-gold">•</span> Photocopying of books is limited to 15 pages only.</li>
