                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Library staff roam around for security purposes.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> A security gate is placed at the entrance of the library to alert the librarian of users who would bring out library materials without permission.</li>
