                                        <p class="text-slate-600 font-bold text-xs mb-3">The following acts of misconduct are covered by the FEU Institute of Technology Student Handbook which provides for corresponding sanction:</p>
                                        <ul class="text-slate-600 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed list-none">
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Pilferage, defacement and mutilations of any library materials.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Dishonesty in the form of bringing out library materials without permission.</li>
                                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-2 text-feu-green">•</span> Discourtesy or any misdemeanour towards any Library Associate.</li>
                                        </ul>
